Behavior now

Editor has AI toolbar:
Brief -> Generate
Instruction + Preserve Voice -> Rewrite (3 candidates)
Provider override dropdown (default provider fallback)
Rewrite returns 3 candidates with unified diff and manual “Apply to Editor”.
Each generate/rewrite call is persisted to ai_runs with status/latency/error.
AISettings supports setting/clearing default provider.
AI run history is displayed in Editor.
